snippet.title: Bazoik Gameplay
snippet.description:
Download at itch.io! https://billy2600.itch.io/bazoik


This is a little over a minute of gameplay from our game Bazoik. Bazoik is a clone of the arcade game Berzerk, and features fast-paced arcade action.
